      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This F87 M2 Competition represents a benchmark in mechanical preservation. Under the carbon fiber strut brace sits the S55 twin-turbocharged inline-six, featuring a closed-deck block and a forged crankshaft for maximum torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and an electronically controlled Active M Differential, ensuring surgical power delivery. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with zero play in the ball joints, and the high-performance 6-piston front calipers show no signs of thermal stress. Finished in showroom-quality paint with documented maintenance and consistent oil analysis, this is a turnkey specimen for the discerning purist.",
