      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior finish retains its original deep luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats show absolutely no signs of bolster wear, and the original floor mats are included. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive, gap-free service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians. It has never been driven in inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between used and brand-new. All original keys, manuals, and service receipts are included in the sale.",
